Also -

- All the GETxxxDATE (eg GETBIRTHDATE) commands have a new option to return
  dates in a "numeric" string format. This eliminates any problems due to
  non-English dates. Refer to @{" GETxxxDATE Numeric Format " LINK GETXXXNUMERIC} for further
  information.

- All the PUTxxxDATE (eg PUTBIRTHDATE) commands have a new ability to set
  dates using a "numeric" string format. This eliminates any problems due
  to non-English dates. Refer to @{" PUTxxxDATE Numeric Format " LINK PUTXXXNUMERIC} for further
  information.

@ENDNODE

