##
## "GETCHILD"
##

@NODE getchild "GETCHILD"
GETCHILD command:

Obtain the IRN (Individual Record Number) for the specified child of the
specified family

	SYNTAX:	GETCHILD CurrentFGRN ChildNum

	where:  'CurrentFGRN' is the FGRN of the family
	        of interest in the Scion database, and

	        'ChildNum' is the "number" of the specified child
		(ie. 0, 1, 2, etc. for first, second, third, etc. child)

	result: The IRN (Individual Record Number) for the specified
		child "number" of the specified family

	The result is returned in the ARexx variable RESULT.

EXAMPLE USAGE:
	MyPort = "SCIONGEN"	/* Point at Scion Genealogist port */
	Address value MyPort	/* Change ARexx address to that port */
	MyFGRN = 5		/* Set MyFGRN to family 5 */
	ChildNum = 2		/* Examine 3rd child of this family */
	GETCHILD MyFGRN ChildNum	/* Issue command */
	Say "IRN of family's child number" ChildNum ":" RESULT
@ENDNODE

##
## "GETFILEVERSION"
##

@NODE getfileversion "GETFILEVERSION"
GETFILEVERSION command:

Obtain the current database file version set by Scion.

	SYNTAX:	GETFILEVERSION

	result: The current database file version set by Scion.
                Scion will always read databases with version numbers
		less than or equal to this number.

        See also @{" GETDBVERSION " LINK getdbversion}

	The result is returned in the ARexx variable RESULT.

EXAMPLE USAGE:
	MyPort = "SCIONGEN"	/* Point at Scion Genealogist port */
	Address value MyPort	/* Change ARexx address to that port */
	GETFILEVERSION		/* Issue command to Scion Genealogist */
	Say "Current Scion database file version:" RESULT
@ENDNODE

##
## "GETDBVERSION"
##

@NODE getdbversion "GETDBVERSION"
GETDBVERSION command:

Obtain the version number of the database currently loaded into Scion

	SYNTAX:	GETDBVERSION

	result: The version number of the database currently loaded into
                Scion.

        See also @{" GETFILEVERSION " LINK getfileversion}

	The result is returned in the ARexx variable RESULT.

EXAMPLE USAGE:
	MyPort = "SCIONGEN"	/* Point at Scion Genealogist port */
	Address value MyPort	/* Change ARexx address to that port */
	GETDBVERSION		/* Issue command to Scion Genealogist */
	Say "Currently loaded database file version:" RESULT
@ENDNODE

