@NODE gettxtviewer "GETTXTVIEWER"
GETTXTVIEWER command:			(V5)

Obtain the full path/filename of the user-defined text viewer.
If the viewer is undefined, returns an "empty" string.

	SYNTAX:	GETTXTVIEWER

EXAMPLE USAGE:
	MyPort = "SCIONGEN"	/* Point at Scion Genealogist port */
