## "GETSNDPLAYER"
##

@NODE GETSNDPLAYER "GETSNDPLAYER"
GETSNDPLAYER command:			(V5)

Obtain the full path/filename of the user-defined sound file player.
If the player is undefined, returns an "empty" string.

	SYNTAX:	GETSNDPLAYER

EXAMPLE USAGE:
